Description: The OpenBangsamoro initiative supports the use of open statistical, 
    geospatial, and administrative data for transparent, accountable, and 
    participatory decision-making as the Autonomous Region in Muslim Mindanao 
    (ARMM) transforms into the Bangsamoro Autonomous Region in Muslim Mindanao.
